6. Gift Cards
Last updated: November 27, 2020
Where can I buy a Gift Card?
You can buy Franco Manca Gift Cards from all our pizzerias in the UK, or you can buy them
online
.
How do I activate my Gift Card?
This will automatically be activated when you purchase it.
How do I register my Gift Card?
Register your card at
fmgiftcard.co.uk
to check your balance and ensure balance protection in case your card is lost, stolen or damaged. You will need the long card number and the pin on the card in order to register.
How much do Gift Cards cost?
It is up to you how much money you load on to the Gift Card, it can be any value from £10 to £50.
When I purchased my Gift Card I was given a receipt, do I need to include this receipt with the Gift Card to tell my recipient how much is on the card?
No, you do not need to include the receipt as this is not needed for redemption, however it’s worth holding onto the receipt yourself in case you need to
contact us
.
Can I add more money on to my Gift Card?
Yes you can. Simply head to your local pizzeria and ask one of our team to top up.
Do I have to spend the full value on my Gift Card all in one go?
No, you may make as many transactions as you like until the value on the card is spent.
Can I use my Gift Card for online ordering/ click and collect?
No, unfortunately our Gift Cards cannot currently be used for
Order & Collect
or on Delivery platforms.
If I don’t have enough money on my Gift Card to cover the whole of my bill can I part pay with the Gift Card?
Yes, you can pay as much as you like from your Gift Card. For example if you have £10 on your Gift Card and your bill is £20 you can pay £5 from the Gift Card and pay the remaining £15 in cash or with a debit or credit card.
Franco Manca Gift Card Terms & Conditions
This card can be used by the holder as part or full payment directly at any Franco Manca restaurant in the UK mainland only. Not valid on Order & Collect, Deliveroo & Uber Eats. Please present this card when paying. This card cannot be used to pay tips or gratuities.
This card cannot be refunded or exchanged in part or as whole for cash or credit. No change will be given, though any balance may be applied to future purchases, provided that the card has not expired.
Register this card at fmgiftcard.com/register to check balance and ensure balance protection in case your card is lost, stolen or damaged. Franco Manca cannot be held liable for balances of credit on any unregistered card.
This card will expire 12 months from date of purchase or most recent top up and any balance remaining on expiry will be reduced to nil and forfeited.
Franco Manca may refuse the sale of alcohol or any other item to a gift card holder at its sole discretion.
This gift card can be activated with a minimum value of £10.
This card is not a credit or debit card.
Franco Manca reserves the right to amend the terms & conditions of this service at any time.
