Franco Manca Blue Light Card & Defence Discount Card Terms & Conditions
You can use your Blue Light Card or Defence Discount Card at any Franco Manca pizzeria in the UK to claim 25% off food, as further described in these Terms and Conditions. The Franco Manca discount is valid for dine in and takeaway only. The cards are not valid on the Click and Collect, Deliveroo, Uber Eats and Just Eat platforms.
1. To redeem a discount, the Blue Light Card/Defence Discount Card holder must present a the card to their server. The discount redeemed entitles the holder to 25% off their total food bill on Mondays, Tuesdays and Wednesdays. Limited to 4 people per card.
2. The start date for this offer is 11:30am on 18th June 2018.
3. To claim discount at Franco Manca using the Blue Light Card or Defence Discount Service card, you must be aged 16 or over and a resident in the UK. Proof of age may be required when using the Blue Light card and you must act truthfully when providing details of your age.
4. Certain items including Franco Manca gift cards and set menu promotions do not count towards Qualifying Purchases. To receive the discount, a valid Blue Light Card or Defence Discount Service card must be presented to your server at the time of payment.  If you are unsure whether an item qualifies, please speak to a member of staff.
5. A maximum of one Blue Light Card or Defence Discount card can be used on any total food bill.
6. A Blue Light Card or Defence Discount card discount cannot be used in conjunction with any other offer.
7. The discount balances redeemed using a Blue Light Card or Defence Discount Service card in a Franco Manca pizzeria cannot be exchanged for cash.
8. Franco Manca reserves the right to refuse to accept a Blue Light Card or Defence Discount card, and/or to limit the use of either card which it deems to have been tampered with, duplicated, damaged or which otherwise is suspected to be affected by fraud, misconduct or unauthorised use. Franco Manca may take any action it may deem appropriate if it suspects fraud, misconduct or unauthorised use of a Blue Light Card or Defence Discount Service card.
9. Blue Light Cards and Defence Discount Service Cards can only be used at Franco Manca pizzerias within the United Kingdom.
